NOTE TARGET PIXEL
MODE
LINK 800

NOTE SET COLLISION VAL
NOTE TO DIFFERENTIATE
NOTE FROM OTHER SPRITES
COPY 100 GP
COPY 50 CO

NOTE MOVE TO A RANDOM
NOTE PLACE ON THE SCREEN
MARK MOVE_POS
RAND 0 100 GX
RAND 0 080 GY

MARK WAIT_FOR_COLLISION
WAIT
NOTE CONTINUE WAITING IF
NOTE NOT COLLIDED WITH
NOTE ANYTHING
TEST CI = -9999
TJMP WAIT_FOR_COLLISION

NOTE INCREMENT SCORE
COPY 1 M
NOTE RE-PLACE AND RESUME
JUMP MOVE_POS